io.spine.testing

Class ClassTest<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.testing.ClassTest<C>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - the class under the tests
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SingletonTest, UtilityClassTest

    public abstract class ClassTest<C>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base for test suites that test a class (e.g. static methods) rather than an object.
